Set Field-Level Security to Analytics Integration User

Give the Analytics Integration users access to all the fields that are used in the app.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Developer Edition and for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions

From Setup, enter the object name.
Select Fields & Relationships.
Select Set Field-Level Security.
For the Analytics Cloud Integration User profile, select Visible, and then save your changes.
Repeat these steps for all fields on all objects that the app uses.
title: Setting Field-Level Security for Analytics Integration Users
